The paper discusses knowledge graph embedding methods, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) applications such as semantic search engines, question-answering systems, and recommender systems. The paper also discusses the use of embedding vectors in data analysis, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper focuses on the analysis and comparison of different models, which is a common topic in database systems (cs.DB).
